  "title": "Publish v2 docs to github pages",
  "body": "* `$ yarn dev` -> now runs dev app & docs\r\n* `$ yarn docs:publish` -> build for production & publish docs to gh-pages\r\n* `$ yarn docs:build:dev` -> build locally docs (useful for debugging purpose & used by netlify)\r\n\r\nDocs are now built in the `/docs` root folder for any env (no more `/docs` and `/docs-preview`)",
